duties_responsibilities.duty: Identify and qualify business opportunities and develop strategies to resolve technical blockers

Demonstrate and prototype Google Cloud product integrations and guide customers through application modernization and migration to hybrid-cloud computing models
Recommend integration strategies, enterprise architectures, platforms, and application infrastructure for implementing solutions on Google Cloud
Travel to customer sites, conferences, and related events as required
